o - 4 : 0; i < hash.length(); i += 4) {\n            val = (int)(((val << 16) + Integer.parseInt(hash.substring((int) i, (int) i + 4), 16)) % mod);\n        }\n\n        return val == 0;\n    }\n\n    private static double generateCrashPoint(String seed, String salt) throws Exception {\n        String hash = encode(seed, salt);\n\n        double hs = 100 / (0.05 * 100);\n\n        if (isCrashHashDivisible(hash, hs)) {\n            return 100;\n        }\n\n        long h = Long.parseLong(hash.substring(0, 52 / 4), 16);\n        double e = Math.pow(2, 52);\n\n        return Math.floor((100 * e - h) / (e - h));\n    }\n\n    public static void main(String[] args) throws Exception {\n        String privateSeed = "";\n\n        String publicSeed = "";\n\n        double expectedCrashpoint = generateCrashPoint(privateSeed, publicSeed);\n\n        System.out.println("The crashpoint for this round is " + expectedCrashpoint / 100.0);\n\n    }\n}\n  ',
